  <summary date="2023-10-11T15:45:25Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Background Check Completion Act of 2023

This bill prohibits a licensed gun dealer from transferring a firearm to an unlicensed person prior to the completion of a background check. Current law permits a licensed gun dealer to transfer a firearm to an unlicensed person if a submitted background check remains incomplete after three business days.</summary>
